
1: go to translation, there you must do the following
    a. go to terminal       cd translation
    b. create virtual environment   python -m venv flask
    c. activate virtual environment     .\flask\Scripts\Activate
    d. install dependencies
        pip install Flask
        pip install googletrans
    e. run the server python flaskapp.py

2: Open a new terminal, keep the old one running
    a. create virtual environment      python -m venv translator
    b. activate virtual environment         .\translator\Scripts\Activate
    c.install dependencies
         pip install openai
          pip install requests
          pip install python-docx


    d. instert api key into translator.py for openai
    e. choose the file location of the text to be translated and where the translation should be stored
    f. run it             python translator.py
